│  handling, integration into larger application logic, etc., before use. The  │
│  provided regex pattern does not cover all possible vulnerabilities but can  │
│  serve as a starting point.                                                  │
│                                                                              │
│  Tests would typically include unit tests for each static method             │
│  (`BASE_DIR`, `is_valid_path()`, and any regular expression-based methods),  │
