│  #!/usr/bin/env python3                                                      │
│                                                                              │
│  """                                                                         │
│  Create executive_summary_generator.py utility that generates an executive   │
│  summary summarizing various security scans.                                 │
│  This utility is designed to be production-ready with comprehensive          │
│  documentation, error handling, and testing. It can generate reports for     │
│  multiple services like Nmap, OpenVAS, or even custom scans.                 │
│                                                                              │
│  Example Usage:                                                              │
│  ```python                                                                   │
│  import exec_summary_generator                                               │
