│  primary requirements and can be further enhanced for increased fault        │
│  tolerance, customization, and robustness according to specific use cases    │
│  or business needs. In particular, it does not implement all possible        │
│  mitigations against XML External Entities (XXE) attacks but provides        │
│  context on how one might go about creating such a tool. For comprehensive   │
│  scanning, consider incorporating more advanced techniques such as           │
│  tokenization of references, blocking known malicious URLs or domains, and   │
